quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,Sâd. Nge’Kur’ân enenkumbuzo
  38,2,Nakanye abo bangakholwayo basekuphikiseni okuyinkukhumalo yobuxoki
  38,3,Zingaphi izizukulwana eSazitshabalalisayo ngaphambili kunabo! Ke kaloku zakhala kwaba kungasekho xesha lakubaleka
  38,4,"Kananjalo (ama-Arabhu angakholwayo) amangalisekile kukuba kufike uMlumkisi kuwo ephuma phakathi kwawo. Yaye abangakholwayo bathi: “Lo (Mprofeti uMuhammad) ngumenzi wemilingo, ixoki"
  38,5,"Ingaba udibanise oothixo bonke baba nguthixo omnye? Inene, yinto engummangaliso le"
  38,6,"Ke kaloku abaziinkokeli phakathi kwabo bahamba besithi: “Nina hlalani nibambelele koothixo benu! Inene le yinto equlunqwe (ngokuchasene nani)"
  38,7,"Asizanga siyive into (enjengale) kwinkolo yale mihla (ubuKhristu), asintoyimbilengaphandlekokubangumqambo"
  38,8,"Ingaba iNkumbuzo1 ityhilwe kuye (yedwa) phakathi kwethu?” Unotshe, eneneni bona basezintandabuzweni ngeNkumbuzo yaM! Nakanye, abakasingcamli isohlwayo (saM)"
  38,9,"Makube mhlawumbi banoovimba benceba yeNkosi yakho, uSomandla, uMboneleli wokwenene"
  38,10,Okanye mhlawumbi ulongamelo lwamazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi kuwo lolwabo? Ukuba kunjalo ke mabanyuke kaloku (beze emazulwini) ngeendlela (zabo)
  38,11,Baya kuba ngumkhosi owoyisiweyo njengemikhosi yobumbano yamandulo (eyoyiswayo)
  38,12,Phambi kwabo (baninzi) abaphikisa (abathunywa) abantu bakwaNûh nabakwa’Ad; nabakwaFir’awn umfo wezibonda (awayesohlwaya ngazo abantu)
  38,13,NabakwaThamûd nabantu bakwaLût nabemi baseziNkunini abo ke yayingabantu bobumbano
  38,14,Akukho namnye kubo ongazanga abaphike abaThunywa. Ngoko ke isohlwayo saM sathetheleleka
  38,15,Aba ke balindele isithonga esinye kuphela seXilongo akuyi kubakho kuthotha nasiphelo kuso
  38,16,"Bathi: “Nkosi yethu! Khawulezisa (Usinike iiNcwadi zezenzo zethu ezilungileyo nezigwenxa ukuze sizibone) ingekafiki iMini yamatyala"
  38,17,"Yibanomondewena(Muhammad) mayelanokobakuthethayo, ukhumbule kananjalo isiCaka seThu uDâwûd wanyamezela ngamandla. Inene yena wayehlala ebuyela (kuThi) ngezinto zonke (awayezenza), enenguquko"
  38,18,Senza iintaba ukuba zizukise iindumiso zeThu kunye naye (uDâwûd) emva kwemini nasekuphumeni kwelanga kude kube semini emaqanda
  38,19,"Zenza njalo neentaka zahlangana, zamthobela zonke (uDâwûd)"
  38,20,Senza ubukumkani bakhe baba namandla Samnika ubulumko nokugweba ngokulungileyo ngentetho nangokuthabatha isigqibo
  38,21,Ingaba iindaba zababangisani ababini zifikile na kuwe? Xa batsiba udonga lwendawo yakhe yokuthandazela
  38,22,"Bathi bakungena kuye uDâwûd wothuka. Bathi bona: “Musa ukoyika, (thina singabantu ababangisanayo) ababini, omnye kuthi wone omnye, ngoko ke gweba phakathi kwethu ngenyaniso. Ungasiphathi ngentswela bulungisa, usikhokelele kananjalo eNdleleni elungileyo.”"
  38,23,"(Omnye kubo wathi): “Umzalwana wam lo unezimvu ezingamashumi asithoba anethoba, ndibe mna ndinenye kuphela kodwa (ngoko kunjalo) uthi: ‘Ndinike yona.’ Kwaye uyandongamela ngokuthetha.”"
  38,24,"UDâwûd (engalibazisanga) wathi: “Ukonile ngokufuna imvu yakho ukuba ayongeze kwezakhe. Kambe maninzi amahlulelane acinezelanayo, ngaphandle kwabo bakholwayo, benze izenzo ezilungileyo yaye bambalwa.” Ke kaloku uDâwûd waqikelela okokuba beSimvavanya wacela itarhu eNkosini yakhe, wawa phantsi waqubuda wabuyela kuAllâh ngenguquko"
  38,25,"Samxolela ke ngoko, ukanti okwakhe kukuba kufuphi naThi nendawo yokubuyela (iPaladesi)"
  38,26,"Hini na Dâwûd! Inene wena Sikubekele ukuba ube ngummeli ehlabathini; ngoko ke gweba ngokusenyanisweni, ungalandeli iminqweno yakho ngokuba iya kukuphambukisa eNdleleni ka-Allâh Inene abo baphambukayo eNdleleni ka-Allâh baya kufumana isohlwayo esibuhlungu ngokuba bona baye balibala ngeMini yemibuzo"
  38,27,Kanti ke Asidalanga amazulu nomhlaba nako konke okukuwo ngaphandle kwenjongo! Leyo yingcinga yabo bangakholwayo! Yeha ke kwabo bangakholwayo eMlilweni
  38,28,"Ingaba Siza kuphatha abo bakholwayo, benza izenzo ezilungileyo njengabenzi bobubi emhlabeni okanye Siphathe abo bahlonela uAllâh njengezingcoli"
  38,29,"(Le) yiNcwadi (i’Kur’ân) eSiyithumele kuwe, izele ziintsikelelo, khon’ukuze bacamngcisise ngeeVesi zayo aze namadoda anengqiqo phakathi kwabo akhumbule"
  38,30,Kananjalo uDâwûd Sampha uSulaymân. Esinjani ukulunga sona isiCaka! Inene yena wayehlala ebuyela (kuThi) ngenguquko
  38,31,Kwathi emva kwemini kwakwenziwa umboniso phambi kwakhe wamahashe aqeqeshiweyo omkhosi wokulwa imfazwe
  38,32,"Wathi yena: “Mna ndiye ndathanda (la mahashe) endaweni yokukhumbula iNkosi yam, lada ixesha (lomthandazo wasemva kwemini) laphela, (nelanga) lafihlakala kwisigqubuthelo (sobusuku).”"
  38,33,"Waza wathi: “Waziseni kum wahambahambisa isandla sakhe emilenzeni yawo nasezintanyeni zawo kwada kwaya kuphela umboniso"
  38,34,"Kananjalo Savavanya uSulaymân, Sabeka umzimba (ongenabomi) waza wabuyela (kuAllâh ngenguquko nangentobeko)"
  38,35,"Wathi: “Nkosi yam ndixolele, Undiphe ubukumkani obungasokuze bube bobakhe nabani na emva kwam: inene Wena unguSokupha.”"
  38,36,"Ke kaloku Samenzela ukuba umoya umthobele, wawuvuthuza ngocoselelo, ngokomyalelo wakhe, naphi na apho athanda khona"
  38,37,Kanti namashayâtini (ooSathana) nabo bonke abakhi neendadi
  38,38,Nabanye ababebotshwe ngamakhamandela
  38,39,"(UAllâh Wathi kuSulayman): “Esi sisipho seThu ngoko ke sisebenzise okanye usigcine kuwe, akukho nto iza kubuzwa (kuwe) ngaso.”"
  38,40,"Inene okwakhe kukuba secaleni kweThu, nokubuyela kokulungileyo ePaladesi"
  38,41,"Khumbula kananjalo isicaka seThu uAyyûb ukucela kwakhe eNkosini yakhe (esithi): “Inene uShaytân undifumene ngenkxwaleko nangentuthumbo"
  38,42,"UAllâh Wathi: “Ngqisha emhlabeni ngonyawo lwakho: nanku umthombo wamanzi wokuba uhlambe kuwo, akwasisiselo esipholileyo"
  38,43,"Kananjalo Saphinda Sambuyisela usapho lwakhe, ndawonye nokunye okufana noko njengenceba evela kuThi, nenkumbuzo kwabo baqiqayo"
  38,44,"Uthathe ngesandla sakho isicithi sengca ubethe ngaso (umfazi wakho), ungasaphuli isithembiso sakho. Inene Thina Samfumana (uAyyûb) enomonde, esinjani ukulunga sona isicaka! Inene yena wayesoloko ebuyela (kuThi) ngenguquko"
  38,45,"Khumbula kananjalo isicaka seThu uIbrâhîm, uIs-hâ’k, noYa’kûb (bonke) abo babe namandla (okuSikhonza) nengqiqo (elungileyo) yenkolo"
  38,46,Inene Sabakhetha bona ngokubanika inkumbuzo yekhaya (lasemva kokufa)
  38,47,"Kananjalo bona bakunye naThi, yaye bangabakhethiweyo, abona balungileyo"
  38,48,"Khumbula uIsmâ’îl, uAlyasa’2 noDthul-kifil3, bonke (abo) ngabanye babo balungileyo"
  38,49,Le yinkumbuzo. Yaye inene okwabanyulu iya kuba kukubuyela okulungilelyo kwasePaladesi
  38,50,"E’Adn (eEden), uMyezo omasango awo aya kuvulelwa bona"
  38,51,Phakathi apho baya kungqiyama; apho baya kubiza indyebo yeziqhamo neziselo
  38,52,"Ukanti ecaleni kwabo iya kuba ngabafazi abanyulu abaya kuba bebambe amehlo abo (ukuba anganqweneli bambi ngaphandle kwabayeni babo), benobudala obulinganayo"
  38,53,Oku ke kuko oko nina bamoyikayo uAllâh nithenjiswa ngako ngeMini yamatyala
  38,54,(Kuya kuthiwa kubo)! “Inene le yimbonelelo yeThu kuni engasokuze iphele
  38,55,Oku kunjalo! Ke kaloku kubagabadeli iya kuba kukubuyela okubi (kwaseMlilweni)
  38,56,"EsiHogweni kulapho baza kutsha khona, hayi ukuba mbi kwaloo ndawo yokuphumla (kwabo)"
  38,57,Oku kunjalo! Mabangcamle (isohlwayo) ke ulwelo olubandayo nobubomvu (obuphuma ezilondeni)
  38,58,Nezinye (izohlwayo) ezikwanjalo zidityaniswe zonke
  38,59,Eli liqela Eliza lingxamile kuwe! Akuyi kubakho kwamkeleka kubo Inene bona baza kutsha eMlilweni
  38,60,"(Ababengabalandeli baya kukhala kwabo babalahlekisayo bathi): “Oku kwenu! Akukho kwamkeleka kuni! Nini aba basihlisela oku phezu kwethu (emhlabeni), hayi ububi bale ndawo yokuhlala.!”"
  38,61,"Baya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu! Nabani na owasihlisela oku, mongezele isohlwayo ngokuphindwe kabini eMlilweni!”"
  38,62,"Ke kaloku baya kuthi: “Kwenzeka ntoni na kanye kuthi ukuba singababoni abantu esasidla ngokubabala nabangalunganga"
  38,63,"Ingaba sasibenza izinto zokugculela, okanye mhlawumbi ngamehlo ethu asilelayo ukubabona?”"
  38,64,Inene leyo yinyaniso yokwenene baya kuphikisana abantu boMlilo
  38,65,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Mna ndinguMlumkisi kuphela yaye akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle koAllâh, Omnye, Ongenakuphikiswa"
  38,66,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi kwawo, uSomandla, uMxoleli.”"
  38,67,"Yithi: “Le ‘Kur’ân iziindaba ezinkulu"
  38,68,Ezo nina nizitshikilelayo
  38,69,"Mna andinalwazi lwaziphathazithunywa, xa zazipikisana, zixoxa (ngokudalwa komntu)"
  38,70,"Okutyhiliweyo\tkum\tkuphela\tkoku:\tkukuba\tmna ndinguMlumkisi ocacileyo.”"
  38,71,"Yabona! INkosi yakho yathi kwiingelosi: “Ndiza kudala umntu ngodongwe"
  38,72,"Ekumbumbeni kwaM, Ndamphefumlela umoya wakhe, niya kuwa niqubude kuye ke nina.”"
  38,73,Zaqubuda iingelosi zonke
  38,74,"Ngaphandle koIblîs (uSathana): waba nekratshi waza waba ngomnye wabangakholwayo"
  38,75,"UAllâh Wathi: “Hini na Iblîs! Yintoni na ekuthintelayo ukuba ungaqubudi kulowo Ndimdalileyo ngeZandla zaM zoziBini? Uzingca kakhulu na okanye ungoyena wabaphakamileyo abakhulu kusini na?”"
  38,76,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Mna ndingcono kunaye. Mna Undidale ngomlilo, yena Wamdala ngodongwe.”"
  38,77,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Phuma umke apha; kuba wena ulahliwe"
  38,78,Yaye inene isiqalekiso saM siya kuba phezu kwakho kude kube yiMini yoMgwebo”
  38,79,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Nkosi yam! Ndimele kude kube yiMini yoVuko lwabafileyo.”"
  38,80,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Inene wena ungomnye wabo bamelweyo"
  38,81,Kude kube lixesha elimisiweyo.”
  38,82,"(UIblîs)\twathi:\t“Ngamandla\taKho,\tinene\tmna\tndiya kubalahlekisa bonke"
  38,83,Ngaphandle kwezicaka zaKho ezikhethekileyo phakathi kwabo.”
  38,84,"(UAllâh) Wathi: “Yinyaniso (leyo) yaye inyaniso Ndithi (kuwe)"
  38,85,Ndiya kuzalisa isiHogo ngawe ndawonye nabo (bantu) balandela wena.”
  38,86,"Yithi (Muhammad): “Akukho ntlawuliso ndinibiza yona ngale (‘Kur’ân), ndingenguye nomnye wabaqambi (bobuxoki)"
  38,87,Yona le (‘Kur’ân) yinkumbuzo yendalo yonke
  38,88,Ke kaloku niza kuyazi inyaniso emveni kwethuba.”